# Training-time artefacts — never committed.
#
# - oww_data/   the negatives slice + validation .npy (~1.7 GB total)
# - oww_output/ generated positive WAVs (~500 files) and any training
#               intermediates (the trained .onnx is COPIED into
#               app/wake/models/hey_cj.onnx, which IS committed)
# - g2_clips/, g2b_clips/, g2c_clips/, g3_pretrim_clips/ — listening tests
# - Any *.npy or *.wav that accidentally gets dropped here
#
# The trained model itself lives in app/wake/models/ and IS committed.

oww_data/
oww_output/
g2_clips/
g2b_clips/
g2c_clips/
g3_pretrim_clips/
*.npy
*.wav

# Training-run logs (e.g. g5_train_v2.log) — verbose tqdm + warnings,
# regenerated on every run.
*.log
